        </div>
        <div class="uvt-depth-bar__track">
          <div class="uvt-depth-bar__fill uvt-depth-bar__fill--fail" style="width: 25%;"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="uvt-depth-bar__verdict">Warms skin only — gone when removed</div>
      </div>

      <div class="uvt-depth-bar">
        <div class="uvt-depth-bar__header">
          <span class="uvt-depth-bar__name">TENS Units</span>
          <span class="uvt-depth-bar__value">~2-3mm</span>
        </div>
        <div class="uvt-depth-bar__track">
          <div class="uvt-depth-bar__fill uvt-depth-bar__fill--fail" style="width: 31%;"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="uvt-depth-bar__verdict">Distracts nerves — pain returns when off</div>
      </div>

      <div class="uvt-depth-bar">
        <div class="uvt-depth-bar__header">
          <span class="uvt-depth-bar__name">[BRAND]™ Infrared Belt</span>
          <span class="uvt-depth-bar__value" style="color: #2ecc71; font-size: 16px;">8mm</span>
        </div>
        <div class="uvt-depth-bar__track">
          <div class="uvt-depth-bar__fill uvt-depth-bar__fill--pass" style="width: 100%;"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="uvt-depth-bar__verdict uvt-depth-bar__verdict--pass">Reaches muscles, joints & nerve tissue</div>
      </div>

      <div class="uvt-depth__zone">
        <span class="uvt-depth__zone-label">Chronic pain origin: 5–8mm deep</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Us vs Them comparison rows (#58 pattern) {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="uvt-compare">
      <div class="uvt-compare__header">
        <div class="uvt-compare__header-us">[BRAND]™ Belt</div>
        <div class="uvt-compare__header-them">Everything Else</div>
      </div>
      <div class="uvt-row">
        <div class="uvt-row__us">Penetrates 8mm deep into tissue</div>
        <div class="uvt-row__them">Surface-level only (1-3mm)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="uvt-row">
        <div class="uvt-row__us">Relief lasts hours after use</div>
        <div class="uvt-row__them">Pain returns immediately</div>
      </div>
      <div class="uvt-row">
        <div class="uvt-row__us">Clinically proven wavelengths</div>
        <div class="uvt-row__them">No clinical evidence</div>
      </div>
      <div class="uvt-row">
        <div class="uvt-row__us">Addresses root inflammation</div>
        <div class="uvt-row__them">Masks symptoms only</div>
      </div>
      <div class="uvt-row">
        <div class="uvt-row__us">One device, all joints</div>
        <div class="uvt-row__them">Different product for each area</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {%- comment -%} Reframe text — graduated belief shift {%- endcomment -%}
    <div class="uvt-reframe">
      <p class="uvt-reframe__text">
        You didn't fail. You didn't pick wrong. <strong>You tried one depth eleven times in different packaging.</strong>
      </p>
      <p class="uvt-reframe__text">
        The [BRAND]™ Infrared Belt uses <strong>660nm + 850nm dual wavelengths</strong> that penetrate <strong>8mm into tissue</strong> — past the skin, past the surface, into the deep muscle and joint layer where inflammation builds and nerves get compressed.
      </p>
      <p class="uvt-reframe__text uvt-reframe__text--highlight">
        It's like watering a plant by misting the leaves vs. soaking the roots. For the first time, you can reach where the pain actually lives — at home.
      </p>
    </div>

    <a class="uvt-section__cta" href="{{ section.settings.cta_url | default: '#product-hero' }}">
      {{ section.settings.cta_text | default: 'TRY IT RISK-FREE' }}
    </a>
    <p class="uvt-section__cta-sub">60-day money-back guarantee with every order</p>
  </div>
</div>

